{"tid":2056881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"美國設計師:\"TWICE MV抄襲,正在組建法務組應對。","createTime":"2020-06-09T04:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T06:12:13.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0793af39e2a26c743090ad753739d95f4eb563ae","tid":2056881,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"【xportsnews獨家】<br />\n美國造型藝術作家Davies McCarty 就組合TWICE的MV中造型物剽竊爭議表明了立場.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;我們法務組和我深刻地認為這是剽竊(plagiarism)。&quot; 對有關情況他們認為&quot;剽竊&quot;, 並明確表示成立法務小組.<br />\n&quot;希望他們能做正直的(honorable)的工作, 和我們一同解決這個問題&quot;<br />\n<br />\n此前，Davis McCarty表示TWICE《MORE &amp; MORE》MV中出現的造型物與自己於2016年創作的&ldquo;Pulse Portal&rdquo;造型物相似。 JYP娛樂對此表示:&ldquo;本公司3日上午通過報導得知《MORE &amp; MORE》MV中出現的造型物與已有的特定作品相似的事實，要求MV製作公司通過與原作作者對話圓滿解決該問題。本公司作為推出藝術家作品的公司，將完善驗證系統杜絕類似事件再次發生。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc676a8296523e7ccfc2bd521b33b9765931c38d","tid":2056881,"uid":138658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a5a2364541c2f0b5c309c1a1b13eac2ddfe309","tid":2056881,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26c8423a3d99710b789720322f398cb3bfa30e3","tid":2056881,"uid":3204,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"賣晒佢哋做雞啦"},{"p